      h1 Yusuke Kido
      p
        | I’m a designer, developer, and NLPer.
        | I also enjoy building things such as a bed, desk, and keyboard, as a hobby.

  section
    .upper-right
      h1 As a developer
      p
        | I have wide experience in various fields of software engineering,
        | from Japan’s No.1 dating app <a href="https://www.pairs.lv/">Pairs</a> to <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/windows">Microsoft Windows</a>.
        | I also was involved in launching data analysis/machine learning projects at <a href="https://eure.jp/">eureka</a> and <a href="https://www.vorkers.com/">Vorkers</a>.
        | Now I’m working as CTO at <a href="https://www.legalscape.co.jp/">Legalscape</a>.

  section
    .upper-right
      h1 As a designer
      p
        | I studied design at <a href="https://school.dhw.co.jp/">Digital Hollywood Tokyo</a>.
        | I majored in UI/UX design, and my main interest is in creating UIs that anyone can make use of.
        | I also learned various topics in design, such as graphic design, web design, and creative coding.

  section
